{"tid":956774,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢個世界唔比種族歧視?","createTime":"2018-12-26T14:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T03:51:36.000Z","uid":14503,"like":51,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"38afacaac20b37fcb17b3c32bb603c4fd98db27d","tid":956774,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"例如我見到D阿差樣又唔同我地, 身又有陣味, 又狡猾又污穢又成日犯罪, 總之印象就係唔好.<br />\n咁點解唔可以歧視佢地, 選擇唔同佢地接觸, 唔同枱食飯, 唔同佢地一齊工作, 點解唔就係要比人話種族歧視? 點解就係唔岩?"},{"pid":"b25c2414451a156f7f9b3f9ff9b94a0b7a1460ef","tid":956774,"uid":16719,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"種族歧視係上世紀根本係常態，甚至有好多學者、教會同優生學證據去support。睇康有為《大同書》都視黑人同棕色人係次等"},{"pid":"feddba01d9240dc4951396cedc6e21950ada43ff","tid":956774,"uid":37869,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:12:40.000Z","msg":"聽電台記得陶傑講過 內容類似係咁<br />\n如果你夜晚要經過條巷<br />\n入面有幾個南亞人係到<br />\n你敢唔敢行入去？<br />\n你唔敢係咪歧視佢地"},{"pid":"c25024a1e25e402ba41ff8287da5c32781e6dae3","tid":956774,"uid":213441,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"老老實實 非洲黑婆av 無人睇 算唔算歧視nigget"},{"pid":"5d37ee41f70273280fb537da06da8e1f0268c245","tid":956774,"uid":14503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"我個問題唔係XXX算唔算歧視<br />\n而係點解唔可以歧視?"},{"pid":"da565a302762a654322665c94757d8c404977e84","tid":956774,"uid":28624,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:24:59.000Z","msg":"因為左膠既垃圾政治正確<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔做好自己本身<br />\n人地於是唔鐘意佢<br />\n就話人歧視佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a2a9109d0e9c46c4241a75785b2e21e678e095","tid":956774,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38afacaac20b37fcb17b3c32bb603c4fd98db27d","tid":956774,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"